家银行流水接近4亿 于是因为这样的服务态度，sunwear决定把钱全部取走，放到别的银行。另外，他称比较传统喜欢看现金，所以要全部取成现金拿走。由于数额较大所以不能一次全部取走几千万，所以只能分批取，今天先取500万。不仅取钱，sunwear还因为上海银行的服务态度，要求工作人员进行清点防止缺斤短两，毕竟离柜概不负责。 sunwear 还给网友科普了一下，清点500万并从柜台拿出来一共需要2个小时（两个人+一台点钞机）。"},"attached_info":"Cj8IhruViej4hfIWEAMaCDcxODAwNzYwIKfTq4sGMEA4iQhAAXIJNDkyODM3MTExeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"1576 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-4674e75652a7c657be7b299196562762_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"2_1634443777.8217258","card_id":"Q_492843584","target":{"id":492843584,"title":"S11 小组赛 B 组出线日 EDG 0:1 不敌 100T 将以小组第二身份出线，你有什么想说的？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/492843584","type":"question","created":1634399142,"answer_count":656,"follower_count":1099,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[18427,154337,159224,699102,778708],"comment_count":53,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8IhruViej4hfIWEAMaCDcxODAyMjExIKbnq4sGMDU4ywhAAnIJNDkyODQzNTg0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"953 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-9de8320453bca9d27398c63174354c6e_720w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"3_1634443777.82221","card_id":"Q_492632606","target":{"id":492632606,"title":"如何看待小学 37 名家长联名要求 7 岁女孩转学？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/492632606","type":"question","created":1634301356,"answer_count":1202,"follower_count":5716,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[4719,8015,24166,26804,89346],"comment_count":202,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"“你为什么不开心呀？” “因为没有人跟我玩啊… 之前我跟他们玩得很开心的。” “所以你现在不开心了？” “是的，我不想去上学。” “你觉得学校对你伤害太大了，是吗？” 妞妞（化名）用力点点头。 ——这是